Sentencas: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-d(LCNT) perovskite oxide was investigated as an anode functional layer (AFL) for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-das an anode functional layer for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The surface exsolved Ni nano particles on LCNT scaffold enlarged electrochemically active triple phase boundaries (TPBs) without any agglomeration and mechanical failure.
Titulo: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-das an anode functional layer for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The Ni particles with 60 nm in diameter were homogeneously exsolved from LCNT perovskite.
Titulo: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-das an anode functional layer for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The Ni-YSZ anode supported cell with LCNT anode functional layer (AFL) exhibited a maximum power density of 0.94 W/cm(2), similar to that of the conventional Ni-YSZ AFL cell at 900 degrees
Titulo: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-das an anode functional layer for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: C. The activation polarization resistance of the LCNT AFL cell was effectively reduced compared to that of the Ni-YSZ AFL cell, though it had higher Ohmic resistance due to thicker YSZ electrolyte and lower electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-das an anode functional layer for solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Our study suggests the potential use of LCNT with exsolved nano particles as an active and durable AFL for high-temperature SOFCs.
Titulo: Surface decorated La0.43Ca0.37Ni0.06Ti0.94O3-das an anode functional layer for solid oxide fuel cell applications
